:[/b]<br/><br/>合晶、tcl、law、沪硅都是一起发疯的 感觉硅片这边有什么消息[/quote]<br/>有消息的 有国内订单的小作文<br/>但是更重要是下半年的材料预期<br/>我之前说了  下半年材料会比其他的更好。", "lou": 3021, "content_length": 95, "reply_to": 871111868, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780973071}, {"pid": 871113790, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 67, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-09 10:51", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871113295,45974302,6782]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67201175]憬然又春天[/uid] (2026-06-09 10:48):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:花痴]狼大 光切芯的操作太帅了，加了两天170舒服了[/quote]<br/>我不是说了么  我不是来投资的<br/>我是来炒股挣钱的。我没有信仰<br/>我只想挣钱。", "lou": 3022, "content_length": 71, "reply_to": 871113295, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780973489}, {"pid": 871116614, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 76, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-09 11:11", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "随便反包昨天亏损<br/>你们呢", "lou": 3023, "content_length": 22, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780974678}, {"pid": 871117052, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 76, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-09 11:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "现在你们自己要换位思考<br/>在这种是个人都知道要反弹的日子里  你手上如果不是科技 现在是什么状态。", "lou": 3024, "content_length": 88, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780974874}, {"pid": 871119018, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 50, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-09 11:28", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871118398,45974302,6790]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=25646105]luyifan19941107[/uid] (2026-06-09 11:24):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，下半年AIDC还看吗[/quote]<br/>看的  但是做华为链的AIDC 其他AIDC没卡了  我做和华为有关系的", "lou": 3025, "content_length": 59, "reply_to": 871118398, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780975694}, {"pid": 871119591, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-09 11:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871118972,45974302,6791]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=43260687]倪晨飞[/uid] (2026-06-09 11:27):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，我不理解，昨天不是反抽卖了吗，今天仓位应该比昨天少，今天涨的也就和昨天跌的差不多，为什么会反包呢？[/quote]<br/>因为我有操作", "lou": 3026, "content_length": 17, "reply_to": 871118972, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780975927}, {"pid": 871130253, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 56, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-09 13:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871130101,45974302,6801]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60220546]知者默[/uid] (2026-06-09 13:02):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，下午谁进来了，不像是老登割肉啊&amp;#129300;[/quote]<br/>你管他是谁 我准备T出去了 我找个日高位我就先出去。<br/>这里肯定要不断的挂点人的  不然涨一点那些人就获利卖了", "lou": 3027, "content_length": 102, "reply_to": 871130101, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780981441}, {"pid": 871131443, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 56, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-09 13:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我反正T完了  目前继续65%-70%底仓等下一次低点机会。我都不急的", "lou": 3028, "content_length": 58, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780982212}, {"pid": 871132039, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 49, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-06-09 13:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=871131622,45974302,6805]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-06-09 13:18):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:哭笑]帅比 我有一个小问题 这个位置挂人 真的能挂住吗[/quote]<br/>挂人很简单，比如一个票  你每次都买在日内最高，可能某一次还卖在日内最低 连续两次你的成本就比平均成本高3个点了 <br/>也就是主力赚了3个点 你才回本<br/>这样主力可以保证你在3个点不会获利卖出。", "lou": 3029, "content_length": 176, "reply_to": 871131622, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1780982611}, {"pid": 871132552, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 28, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "202